        <p class="font-sora text-stone-400 text-xs mt-2">Or browse <a href="/african-grey-parrots-for-sale/" class="text-clay-text underline">our full available birds hub</a> to compare Bery with Roys, Bery, Evie, Elad, and the Jins &amp; Jeni pair.</p>
